4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aiming to become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with standards such as ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, attendees receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The curriculum is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop